window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This Christmas, Santa isn’t the only one that’s coming.</b></p> <p>Holly Klaus is the world’s most infamous monster hunter. The daughter of Santa, she’s sworn to use her magical dagger to defend all children from evil creatures. Her number one target, and the only monster that got away?</p> <p>Krampus.</p> <p>Holly is determined to strike down the infamous creature, until Krampus corners her the night before Christmas Eve. He captures her in combat, dragging Holly against her will into his mysterious lair.</p> <p>Holly expects to be eaten on sight, but Krampus intends to devour her in a much different way. Trapped within Krampus’s realm, Holly discovers the monster she was hunting all along is not only her worst enemy, but also her fated mate.<br> <br> Bonded to Krampus and caught within his claws, Holly must discover the truth about Krampus’s evil plans…and the depths of his dark devotion.<br> <br> <i>Captured by Krampus is a hilarious, short and spicy Christmas monster romance from Megan Linski. Funny, sexy, and full of Yuletide cheer, this unexpected love story will warm more than your heart for the holidays.</i></p>"; 
